                <p>
                    <bold>
                        <italic toggle="yes">5.2.3 Collaboration with cooperation partners.</italic>
                    </bold> In addition to the elective courses and new modules, the training program will leverage collaborations with cooperation partners such as the COST Action CA19130 (
