                    </bold> Network training events are a vital component of the DIGITAL program, designed to foster collaboration, knowledge exchange, and professional development. These events are often combined with larger gatherings that include a diverse array of participants, such as industrial partners, civil society, policymakers, and scholars from outside the network. Specific features include:</p>
